reviewText: If you're okay with hearing some dude breathe, eat loudly and do nothing for an hour then this film might be for you. It's filmed on a freaking FLIP camera, if you remember those from the late 2000s and if all the dead space were edited out this would be a 10 minute film. It would still be bad at 10 minutes but at least I wouldn't be so annoyed. Creep Creepersin is a delusional narcissist for thinking we'd care about him, or his below mediocre film, at all.
